      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ZIPPING KAYLI (1) jumps from box 1 for the first time after placing latest at this track (29.50) in a NG. Strike rate this course and distance strong having won two of three tries. Good beginner assisted by the inside draw. Winning claims. BACK TOMORROW (2) has a strong record here with seven wins and eight placings from 19 starts. Comes off a (29.76) win last time, scoring by half a length in a NG over 520m at this track. Looks a key chance on best figures. KING OF GODS (7) is a talented type progressing through the grades and building a strong record. Has been on speed to score at his last couple of runs. Latest win recorded a handy 29.54 at this track. Solid formlines coming through his last run. Likely to be in the finish. CONSIGLIERE (8) showed great speed to lead all the way last start. Big chance again.",
